title: The International Bad Boys Hour Ep 46: Tupac, Suge Knight and Blood Sacrifices with Doc Willis
description: The International Bad Boys are back in the studio after having their best week yet.  More people dowloaded and listened to the show this past week than ever before.  Thank you to all the International Bad Boys and Girls for all of your support.  The boys welcome Comedy Store favorite Doc Willis to the show. Doc talks about the first time he met Mitzi Shore, kicking with Suge Knight, who shot Tupac, what really went down between Joey Diaz and John Caparulo and the urban legend of Blood Sacrifices.  Please let us know what you think about this episode, positive or negative.  If you like the episode please post and tweet it to all of your friends.  Thank you again for all of the love and support!
